product_description.desc_short:
You've grabbed the crown, now grab the backpack!

Quality 

This sustainably produced premium backpack was made from recycled polyester and leaves no detail unattended. The materials used in production are exceptionally durable and promise impressive longevity.

Sustainability 

Recycled plastic is made, for example, from beverage bottles or collected ocean plastic. This avoids the need to produce new plastic and reduces pollution of the environment. Compared to producing virgin plastic, this process uses up to 50% less energy and saves up to 70% CO2 emissions.
